,Recommended,512220,26299417,"Posted: 29 October, 2016",all,Rinski,"--------------------------UPDATE1 (08 feb 2017 - change recommendation to ""Yes""):--------------------------Ok... Game now costs its money and it is good for one who like dungeon crawler type of games. It is brainless slasher and that's all. But it's still boring and misses something important for me, but I can not say what... >.<1. COMBAT SYSTEMNow Combat system is responsive and has some haptic feedback. And it is good!You can parry arrows with a sword, but I couldn't block another sword hit from orc with my sword. I tried several times, but could not. Was it a bad luck or just feature of the game - I don't know.Combat system is still have an issue for a good combat feeling. I will describe it in the next paragraph.2. AIOk, AI is still stupid as hell. They run towards you, when they in the distance to hit you, they will try to do so. They do not try to run around you to shoot you in the back, they do not move in front of you to land a flank hit. No! Just run towards you, stack in front of you, try to kill you, ???, PROFIT!The MAIN PROBLEM in AI and combat system is that when the orc is too close to you, you can not block its hits. You have to move a little bit backward and then you can block some hits again, but orc will come close in some time and you can not block again...The second problem is that AI can spawn behind your back where you were before, right in front of you in the air. And so on... Not a good thing. It's stange that you moved 10 meters from the spawn portal, kill all orcs in front of you, move 5 more meters and some orcs are already running from behind from spawn portal direction.3. GENERATED LEVELSNow I don't get any collisions. But levels are all the same. They are different because they were generated but in the same time they are all the same because they are generated from the small amount of templates.4. DEVELOPERSThat's the main reason why I recommend this game. I appreciate the fact that developers of this game try to do their best, they communicate with the comunity to make the game better, they support and keep updating their game. That's wonderful! Respect, TricksterDevs!--------------------------REVIEW (nov 2016):--------------------------Well, this game is impossible to play if you have played Vanishing Realms before.- Poor combat system. I couldn't understand when I landed an attack and when not, when I was hit and was not...- Stupid AI. They just run towards you and attack you with one template. That's all.- Buggy level generation system. I had to go through a wall to cointinue progress on level.And so on...P.S. English isn't my native language. Sry for mistakes."
